 </li><li> - new_feature - Readymade Skins-  Category filters were very slow for a nested category Readymade Skins - Apply beautiful info window and listing skins. </li><li> - new_feature - Skin Editor - Easy to use the editor to modify the appearance of the skins. </li><li> -  -  Url Filter - Ability to modify maps appearance using URL parameter.</li></ul><h4>Version 4.0.8</h4><ul><li> - fix - Marker clusters was not working on mobile. </li><li> - fix -  Category filters were very slow for a nested category</li></ul><h4>Version 4.0.7</h4><ul><li> - new_feature - New filter wpgmp_map_lang  added to modify map language using hook.</li><li> - improvement - Missing css for proper info window style like our demo page.</li><li> - improvement - An extra space added to separate multiple taxonomies on infowindow and listing.</li></ul><h4>Version  4.0.6</h4><ul><li> - new_feature - Add Maps using Visual Composer any  where </li><li> - new_feature - Set map\'s center point according to locations assigned</li></ul><h4>Version  4.0.5</h4><ul><li> - improvement - Instructions on the import section updated. Showing selected file name and abiity to import latitude and longitude with \"\" double quotes.</li><li> - new_feature - Gesture handling settings added.</li><li> - fix - Default marker for the post was not showing.</li><li> - improvement - Add Location  link is added on Manage Locations page.</li></ul><h4>Version  4.0.4</h4><ul><li> - new_feature - Settings for min and max zoom level is added.</li><li> - fix - Labels for empty custom fields will be removed.</li><li> - fix - Show info window on user\'s current location is fixed.</li><li> - fix - In some cases, 404 error page on add category is resolved.</li></ul><h4>Version  4.0.3</h4><ul><li> - fix - Missing strings added in the language file.</li><li> - fix - Message on Drawing page was not saving properly.</li><li> - fix - Responsive CSS for GRID for tablets.</li><li> - fix - Tabs was not hiding on page load.</li></ul><h4>Version  4.0.2</h4><ul><li> - fix - Route was not draggable according to backend setting.</li></ul><h4>Version 4.0.1</h4><ul><li> - improvement - Responsive CSS issues fixed </li><li> - new_feature - KML links are refreshed every time.</li><li> - new_feature - fc-hide-mobile class can be used to hide data from infowindow and in the listing for Mobiles/Ipads. </li><li> - fix - Marker category icons was not working. </li></ul><h4>Version 4.0.0</h4><ul><li> - new_feature - Export/Import Maps settings from one site to another site.</li><li> - new_feature - Apply your own color schema by choosing Primary and Secondary Colors. </li><li> - new_feature - Apply ready-made 15 color schema. On one click, you can change overall look on google maps and listing. </li><li> - new_feature - Search within default radius based on user\'s location. </li><li> - new_feature - Show listing order by category priority. </li><li> - new_feature - Show categories in order by category priority. </li><li> - new_feature - Show posts on the map using ACF plugin.</li><li> - new_feature - Display custom fields on infowindow message and listing, added by Advanced Custom Fields (ACF) Plugin. </li><li> - new_feature - Ability to customize Infowindow appearance. </li><li> - new_feature - Display search control on google maps to change position on google maps on frontend. </li><li> - new_feature - Ability to setup map properties according to screen size.</li><li> - new_feature - UI is changed using material color schema. </li><li> - new_feature - ID column is added in export csv to use in updation modified entries. </li><li> - new_feature - Feature to update locations based on location ID using CSV.</li><li> - new_feature - Import CSV without latitude and longitude. Geocoding will be perform to calculate latitude & longitude based on address provided in the csv. </li><li> - new_feature - Setup category priority for each category. Show category listing in priority order. </li><li> - new_feature - Setup featured image for manual location. </li></ul><h4>Version 3.4.5</h4><ul><li> - new_feature - Applied nonce during export feature in the backend.</li><li> - new_feature - Dashboard UI improved.</li></ul>\";}}}s:12:\"translations\";a:0:{}s:9:\"no_update\";a:27:{s:33:\"anything-popup/anything-popup.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":9:{s:2:\"id\";s:28:\"w.org/plugins/anything-popup\";s:4:\"slug\";s:14:\"anything-popup\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:33:\"anything-popup/anything-popup.php\";s:11:\"new_version\";s:3:\"6.4\";s:3:\"url\";s:45:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/anything-popup/\";s:7:\"package\";s:57:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/anything-popup.zip\";s:5:\"icons\";a:2:{s:2:\"2x\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/anything-popup/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=1017466\";s:2:\"1x\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/anything-popup/assets/icon-128x128.png?rev=1017466\";}s:7:\"banners\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:68:\"https://ps.w.org/anything-popup/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=898686\";}s:11:\"banners_rtl\";a:0:{}}s:49:\"chatfuel-customer-chat/chatfuel-customer-chat.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":9:{s:2:\"id\";s:36:\"w.org/plugins/chatfuel-customer-chat\";s:4:\"slug\";s:22:\"chatfuel-customer-chat\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:49:\"chatfuel-customer-chat/chatfuel-customer-chat.php\";s:11:\"new_version\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:3:\"url\";s:53:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chatfuel-customer-chat/\";s:7:\"package\";s:71:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/chatfuel-customer-chat.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:75:\"https://ps.w.org/chatfuel-customer-chat/assets/icon-128x128.png?rev=1799778\";}s:7:\"banners\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/chatfuel-customer-chat/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=1799778\";}s:11:\"banners_rtl\";a:0:{}}s:57:\"chicory-recipe-ingredients/chicory-recipe-ingredients.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":9:{s:2:\"id\";s:40:\"w.org/plugins/chicory-recipe-ingredients\";s:4:\"slug\";s:26:\"chicory-recipe-ingredients\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:57:\"chicory-recipe-ingredients/chicory-recipe-ingredients.php\";s:11:\"new_ve