-crispy-speck-and-pangrattato_2000x1500a_0.jpg?itok=y9Qk_Iq6\" data-800src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/800_1x_/public/images/2015/04/spinach-gnocchi_spinach-spatzli-with-brown-butter-crispy-speck-and-pangrattato_2000x1500a_0.jpg?itok=7BTwJyuh\" data-1000src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/1000_1x_/public/images/2015/04/spinach-gnocchi_spinach-spatzli-with-brown-butter-crispy-speck-and-pangrattato_2000x1500a_0.jpg?itok=OmQhqp4R\" data-2000src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/2000_1x_/public/images/2015/04/spinach-gnocchi_spinach-spatzli-with-brown-butter-crispy-speck-and-pangrattato_2000x1500a_0.jpg?itok=q4kd54Db\" />\r\n<div class=\"caption-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"field-body\">\r\n\r\nNear Italy\'s border with Austria, the food takes on a distinctly Teutonic bent with sptzli, a close Italian cousin of German sptzle.<a class=\"linkTargets-processed\" href=\"https://www.saveur.com/article/recipes/spinach-spatzli-with-brown-butter-crispy-speck-and-pangrattato\">Get the recipe for Spinach Sptzli with Brown Butter, Crispy Speck, and Pangrattato </a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"field-credit\">\r\n\r\nCon Poulos\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"st-block markdown  text-left  \">\r\n<h3><a class=\"linkTargets-processed\" href=\"https://www.saveur.com/strangolapreti-italian-cheese-spinach-bread-crumb-dumpling-recipe\">Strangolapreti</a></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"st-block video    \">\r\n<div class=\"st-video-container SirTrevor-Video-processed preview -mfsgdcbgwjs-sapsr -mfsgdcbgwjs-50-3\" data-st-video-info=\"3a0de1d3006bc95eced4eeed52f40e28\" data-st-video-provider=\"Dailymotion\"><iframe src=\"https://c-8oqtgrjgwu46x24yyyx2efcknaoqvkqpx2eeqo.g00.saveur.com/g00/3_c-8yyy.ucx78gwt.eqo_/c-8OQTGRJGWU46x24jvvrux3ax2fx2fyyy.fcknaoqvkqp.eqox2fgodgfx2fx78kfgqx2fz5box78zax3fcwvqrncax3dhcnugx26owvgx3dhcnugx26wk-uvctv_uetggp_kphqx3dvtwgx26gpfuetggp-gpcdngx3dvtwgx26uvctvx3d2x26u