tion-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"field-body\">\r\n\r\nUnlike the heavy red-sauced lasagnas served in America, this Abruzzo-style version relies on an ethereal egg and tomato sauce that puffs when the lasagna is cooked, giving it a souffl-like appearance.<a class=\"linkTargets-processed\" href=\"https://www.saveur.com/article/recipes/veal-and-spinach-lasagna\">Get the recipe for Veal and Spinach Lasagna </a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"field-credit\">\r\n\r\nRomulo Yanes\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"st-block image    \">\r\n<div id=\"page-11\" class=\"st-page-break\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"media media-element-container media-default full-width shareable\"><img class=\"full-width shareable\" src=\"https://www.saveur.com/g00/3_c-8yyy.ucx78gwt.eqo_/c-8OQTGRJGWU46x24jvvrux3ax2fx2fyyy.ucx78gwt.eqox2fukvgux2fucx78gwt.eqox2fhkngux2fuvangux2f877_3z_x2frwdnkex2fitggp_okpguvtqpg_4222z3722.lrix3fkvqmx3dh75O1S-_x26hex3d72x2c72x26k32e.octmx3dkocig_$/$/$/$/$/$/$/$\" alt=\"Green Minestrone with Kohlrabi, Olives, and Spinach Pesto\" data-50src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/50_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=dU0nfKC6&amp;fc=50,50\" data-75src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/75_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=yIo1Iyej&amp;fc=50,50\" data-100src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/100_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=_XKH8mZY&amp;fc=50,50\" data-150src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/150_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=bvgJs2dI&amp;fc=50,50\" data-200src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/200_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=mrvpG0uh&amp;fc=50,50\" data-250src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/250_1x_/public/green_minestrone_2000x1500.jpg?itok=53JMDiTH&amp;fc=50,50\" data-325src=\"https://www.saveur.com/sites/saveur.com/files/styles/325_1x_/public/green_